# Skill: Prompt Engineering

## Contract
- **Input:** Task description or draft prompt
- **Output:** Optimized prompt with quality score
- **Stateless:** Yes

## Process
1. Analyze task type (generation, analysis, extraction)
2. Apply quality framework (clarity, completeness, testability)
3. Optimize for token efficiency
4. Add few-shot examples if needed
5. Validate against checklist

## Checklist
- [ ] Role defined with expertise
- [ ] Task unambiguous (95%+ clarity)
- [ ] Output format specified
- [ ] Constraints explicit
- [ ] Edge cases covered
